renewed attention and interest to the Games, host cities and important Olympic values \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 making them relevant and meaningful for a new generation.\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Surfing\", \"from\": 4291, \"to\": 4298}, {\"ngram\": \"a modern way\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4315}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic values\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4340}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing's natural focus\", \"from\": 4346, \"to\": 4369}, {\"ngram\": \"youth\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4378}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4380, \"to\": 4389}, {\"ngram\": \"renewed attention\", \"from\": 4402, \"to\": 4419}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4432}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4445}, {\"ngram\": \"host cities\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4458}, {\"ngram\": \"important Olympic values\", \"from\": 4463, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"a new generation\", \"from\": 4532, \"to\": 4548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympism and Olympic values were founded on mindfulness, well-being, and healthy lifestyles.\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4644, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympism and Olympic values\", \"from\": 4552, \"to\": 4579}, {\"ngram\": \"well-being\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"healthy lifestyles\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ethos and lifestyle of surfing, with its connection to the natural environment and promoting social harmony, is helping to bring these principles to life.\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4803, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ethos\", \"from\": 4645, \"to\": 4654}, {\"ngram\": \"lifestyle\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4668}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 4672, \"to\": 4679}, {\"ngram\": \"its connection\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4700}, {\"ngram\": \"the natural environment\", \"from\": 4704, \"to\": 4727}, {\"ngram\": \"social harmony\", \"from\": 4742, \"to\": 4756}, {\"ngram\": \"these principles\", \"from\": 4778, \"to\": 4794}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surfing offers an extraordinary opportunity to create a legacy that not only makes a connection to the contemporary philosophy of sound body and mind, but also serves to remind the world of the Olympic values based on inclusivity, self-improvement, harmony with the environment and excellence.\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 5098, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an extraordinary opportunity\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4848}, {\"ngram\": \"a legacy\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 4867}, {\"ngram\": \"a connection\", \"from\": 4888, \"to\": 4900}, {\"ngram\": \"the contemporary philosophy\", \"from\": 4904, \"to\": 4931}, {\"ngram\": \"sound body\", \"from\": 4935, \"to\": 4945}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 4950, \"to\": 4954}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4982, \"to\": 4991}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic values\", \"from\": 4995, \"to\": 5013}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5034}, {\"ngram\": \"self-improvement\", \"from\": 5036, \"to\": 5052}, {\"ngram\": \"harmony\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5061}, {\"ngram\": \"the environment\", \"from\": 5067, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 5087, \"to\": 5097}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Helping to unite people through surfing and sport Surfing is both a sport and a lifestyle that already has an incredible youth following and appeal \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it fundamentally resonates with young people and helps to unite them through shared passions and common beliefs.\", \"from\": 5100, \"to\": 5365, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5117, \"to\": 5123}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 5132, \"to\": 5139}, {\"ngram\": \"sport Surfing\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5157}, {\"ngram\": \"both a sport\", \"from\": 5161, \"to\": 5173}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifestyle\", \"from\": 5178, \"to\": 5189}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible youth\", \"from\": 5207, \"to\": 5226}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 5284, \"to\": 5296}, {\"ngram\": \"shared passions\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5344}, {\"ngram\": \"common beliefs\", \"from\": 5349, \"to\": 5363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the 35 million surfers in the world, we estimate 14 million are aged 12 to 24.\", \"from\": 5366, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 35 million surfers\", \"from\": 5369, \"to\": 5391}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5395, \"to\": 5404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is incredibly valuable for the Olympic Movement.\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5484, \"end\": 5500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999392465835796, \"rank\": 6.075710757331468e-05, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, surfing prioritizes sustainable living and ocean health and safety \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 a philosophy for life that young people in particular are united on.\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5654, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 5506, \"to\": 5513}, {\"ngram\": \"prioritizes\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5534}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable living and ocean health\", \"from\": 5535, \"to\": 5570}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 5575, \"to\": 5581}, {\"ngram\": \"a philosophy\", \"from\": 5586, \"to\": 5598}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5607}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surfing undoubtedly helps to bring people together and this has been evident here at Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 5656, \"to\": 5752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5691, \"to\": 5697}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 5741, \"to\": 5746}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes, teams and fans enjoy a spiritual, natural connection that is rare in international sport.\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5856, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 5753, \"to\": 5765}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 5767, \"to\": 5772}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 5777, \"to\": 5781}, {\"ngram\": \"a spiritual, natural connection\", \"from\": 5788, \"to\": 5819}, {\"ngram\": \"international sport\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5855}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And surfing goes beyond sport to help connect communities.\", \"from\": 5857, \"to\": 5915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 5861, \"to\": 5868}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 5881, \"to\": 5886}, {\"ngram\": \"communities\", \"from\": 5903, \"to\": 5914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At surfing events, you will often find cultural and social activities, including yoga, live music and sustainability and ocean safety activations among much more \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 ultimately to help encourage self-improvement and wellness for all.\", \"from\": 5916, \"to\": 6149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 5927, \"to\": 5933}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural and social activities\", \"from\": 5955, \"to\": 5985}, {\"ngram\": \"yoga\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6001}, {\"ngram\": \"live music\", \"from\": 6003, \"to\": 6013}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainability\", \"from\": 6018, \"to\": 6032}, {\"ngram\": \"ocean safety\", \"from\": 6037, \"to\": 6049}, {\"ngram\": \"activations\", \"from\": 6050, \"to\": 6061}, {\"ngram\": \"self-improvement\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6127}, {\"ngram\": \"wellness\", \"from\": 6132, \"to\": 6140}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, we strive for a better world through surfing.\", \"from\": 6150, \"to\": 6207, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better world\", \"from\": 6176, \"to\": 6190}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \